    "title": "Container Corporation of India Digital Technologies is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Principal)",
    "description": "Container Corporation of India Digital Technologies, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Warehouse Manager for our Gurgaon operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Container Corporation of India Digital Technologies:\nContainer Corporation of India Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in TMS\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Container Corporation of India Digital Technologies!",
